moves.name: Absorb
moves.battle_effect: The user attacks by draining the target's nutrients. Some of the damage dealt to the target is absorbed by the user to restore their own HP.
moves.secondary_effect: Heals the user by up to 50% of the damage inflicted (75% if Strong style)

moves.name: Accelerock
moves.battle_effect: The user smashes into the target at high speed. This move always goes first.

moves.name: Acid
moves.battle_effect: Opposing Pok√©mon are attacked with a spray of harsh acid. This may also lower their Sp. Def stats.
moves.secondary_effect: May lower opponent's Special Defense one stage.

moves.name: Acid Armor
moves.battle_effect: The user alters its cellular structure to liquefy itself, raising its defensive stats.

moves.name: Acid Spray
moves.battle_effect: The user spits fluid that works to melt the target. This may also lower the target's defensive stats.
moves.secondary_effect: May lower the target's defensive stats by 1 stage

moves.name: Acrobatics
moves.battle_effect: The user nimbly strikes the target. If the user is not holding an item, this attack inflicts massive damage.
moves.secondary_effect: Increases damage by 100% if user is not holding an item.

moves.name: Acupressure
moves.battle_effect: The user applies pressure to stress points, sharply boosting one of its or its allies' stats.
moves.secondary_effect: Raises one of the user's stats randomly by two stages.

moves.name: Aerial Ace
moves.battle_effect: The user confounds the target with speed, then slashes. This attack never misses.

moves.name: Aeroblast
moves.battle_effect: A vortex of air is shot at the target to inflict damage. Critical hits land more easily.
moves.secondary_effect: Has an increased Critical Hit ratio
